  "texts": [
    "Notably, LLMs are still in their most nascent stage of development, meaning any evidence for their success at present only hints at their potential influence to come.",
    "As generative AI becomes increasingly powerful, they could either replace most human experts (e.g., creative individuals and marketing practitioners) or-on a more positive note-empower these experts to expand their skill sets and use AI to elevate their current performance levels.",
